import Veiw from './Veiw.js'; // import icons from '../img/icons'; //Parcel 1 import icons from '../../img/icons.svg'; //Parcel 2 import {Fraction} from 'fractional'; class RecipeView extends Veiw{ _parentElement = document.querySelector('.recipe'); _errorMessage = `We could not find that recipe. Please try another one.`; _message = ''; addhandlerRender (handler) { ['hashchange', 'load'].forEach(ev => window.addEventListener(ev, handler)); } _generateMarkup(){ // console.log(this._data); return `
${this._data.cookingTime} minutes
${this._data.servings} servings

Recipe ingredients

    ${this._data.ingredients.map(this._generateMarkupIntregient).join('')}

How to cook it

This recipe was carefully designed and tested by ${this._data.publisher}. Please check out directions at their website.

Directions
`; } _generateMarkupIntregient(ing) { return `
  • ${ing.quantity ? new Fraction(ing.quantity).toString() : ''}
    ${ing.unit} g ${ing.description}
    • ` } } export default new RecipeView;
